        "description": "Prospective observational registry collecting haematological and pump-performance data from 47 CPB patients. No experimental controls or randomisation were applied; patient allocation followed standard clinical care pathways. Data were de-identified and aggregated for comparison against CFD predictions."
      }
    }
  ],
