    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate agreement with the clinical registry hemolysis data across all five operating points (RH < 1 confirmed; MAE 0.04 RH units). The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The assessment team reviewed the validation evidence, including the observational registry comparison, and concluded that the model is fit for the stated COU. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied at worst-case conditions. Decision: Accepted for regulatory submission.",
